    <p>Audi’s facelifted A5 range is here – in Coupe, Sportback (right) and Cabri­o­let forms.</p>
    <p>With prices start­ing at $199,900, the ex­ec­u­tive A5 is a com­pet­i­tive pack­age. With an ex­ten­sively re­vised ex­te­rior and full LED light­ing, the range is now also fit­ted with an in­fo­tain­ment sys­tem with more fea­tures and higher con­nec­tiv­ity. Its 2-litre turbocharg­ed en­gine is avail­able as a 150hp or 190hp, both paired with a 12-volt “mild hy­brid” sys­tem which con­serves fuel.</p>


